{"tid":1579543,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《921 割席宣言，對恐怖分子首領何君堯計劃於921發動恐襲，誓不低頭》","createTime":"2019-09-18T15:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T11:05:20.000Z","uid":278698,"like":50,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"acb18651d6f8919cb47c7eb11acf2e78ca3f8a6f","tid":1579543,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:26:46.000Z","msg":"有鑑於恐怖分子首領何君堯準備於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十八區發起大型恐襲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n為免香港人受到大量人命傷亡，以及穿著黑衣市民被誤中副車<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反送中示威者九月二十一日會係屋企嘆冷氣，訓覺覺，並不會與恐怖分子發生正面衝突。並與當日衝突者正式割席，任何頻道直播之衝突，打鬥場面均與反送中運動無關</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而參加屯門及元朗行動人仕，必會遵守和平，理性，非暴力的原則。若衝突再起，必是恐怖分子所為。<br />\n<br />\n重申，921各區衝突必定為恐怖分子首領何君堯<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自編自導自演進行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任何人命傷亡，一切責任均在香港警察及恐怖分子何君堯，與反送中前線示威者無關</span></span><br />\n<br />\n本帖正式宣布，對同為香港人的恐怖份子首領何君堯發動恐怖襲擊，屠殺各區市民表示痛心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">面對恐怖份子，眾登巴絲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誓！不！低！頭！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆，拆一貼萬！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j6XHTV3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj6XHTV3.png&h=3d5c458e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d81a916c835c988909b66bc410abf4ab1cc91ca","tid":1579543,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dce64670daaee9fbc0d96e3cae3a71f9aeed534a","tid":1579543,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc38499c1d69b4e543580d8dffa189e320096f5","tid":1579543,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/24/24a9c868bd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2F24%2F24a9c868bd.jpeg&h=ed2a8b69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b0125163b2a7347fe1496e7d5803a3209614d1a","tid":1579543,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:31:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2b1fbdbe75566d87df536aa148cc2057e8b6770d","tid":1579543,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"059363c3a7e0c1fc09cf3e28334d6f487ab63795","tid":1579543,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b336976dfa345582d580f409bc6c64b670c4828","tid":1579543,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"39ecf006fd2f0f534312bd61825d48de48b4c5af","tid":1579543,"uid":259710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"推，921唔好衝突，101先玩大佢"},{"pid":"bedbf7049ed369e6fa606f1897b9f6ca726367c7","tid":1579543,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b647ddee90e73bcecab921fbb87d9ea84e416858","tid":1579543,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:35:03.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"a6090813d682ad0781241726e9f39b89544dc14e","tid":1579543,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:38:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"226fc69cd8d313ad09576c7ee4910ace116dfaea","tid":1579543,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img 